steps.name: When Web app login using providerLoginCrendentails
When I hover on the "Dashboard-All Patient" tab
When I click the Manage Patients option
When I populate data Baby 21 in the "Search" field
When I click on the link text Baby
When I click on the link text Medical Record
When I click on the link text Medications
Then Search and delete duplicate data Auto_Medication
When I click on the button with text New Medication
Then It redirects on the New Medication screen
When I fill Auto_Medication data in medication field
When I fill 1 data in current dose field
When I fill Teaspoon data in measurement field
When I fill Twice data in frequency field
When I fill Day data in interval field
When I fill Consult the doctor before using this medicine data in additional information field
When I select date in start Date field
When I click on the button with text Create
Then Success message Medication Added Succesfully ! appears
